                          {p.netSalary.toLocaleString()}
                       </td>
                     </tr>
                   ))}
                 </tbody>
                 <tfoot className="bg-indigo-950 text-white font-black text-[13px] border-t-4 border-indigo-900 print:bg-slate-100 print:text-black">
                    <tr className="shadow-2xl">
